<tr>
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; line-height:1.3em; vertical-align:middle;"><b>Signature</b><br />
<a href="/wiki/File:Nikola_Tesla_signature.png" class="image" title="Nikola Tesla's signature"><img alt="Nikola Tesla's signature" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/41/Nikola_Tesla_signature.png/128px-Nikola_Tesla_signature.png" width="128" height="23" border="0" /></a></td>
</tr>
