n_W._Howell" title="John W. Howell" class="mw-redirect">John W. Howell</a> (1924)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Harris_J._Ryan" title="Harris J. Ryan">Harris J. Ryan</a> (1924)</span></p>
